lead_paragraph: Defending champion Justin Thomas endured a terrible start to the third round of the CIMB Classic after the American faltered with three bogeys and a double bogey to finish with a 1-under 71 Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Lahiri Leads by 4 Shots as Thomas Struggles at CIMB Classic
